&lt;li&gt;Data Analysis: Support analysis of collected data to identify performance trends, collaborating with engineering teams on resolutions.&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Automation: Assist in developing automation scripts for repetitive monitoring and alerting tasks to reduce manual effort.&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Cross-functional Collaboration: Learn from and collaborate with development and operations teams, gaining exposure to cloud and infrastructure best practices across the software development lifecycle.&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Capacity Planning: Assist with capacity planning tasks under senior engineer guidance using observability data.&lt;/li&gt;
