&lt;li&gt;Continuously improve the renewal process and contribute to best practices.&amp;nbsp;&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Stay up-to-date on Redwood Software&#39;s products and services, as well as industry trends.&amp;nbsp;&lt;/li&gt;
